reviewText: Love the family, wish they made more DVD's to buy.
Great concert. Just wish it was available on Blu-Ray.
An amazing family. Such talent. The music, the dance captivate you.  We have watched it twice now and it will be one we watch over and over again.
Lively and entertaining video. I have watched this many times and never tire of it. Looking forward to them coming to the area.

Outstanding preformances and production quality.  Lively delivery of a choice selection of tunes, not all Celtic in origin (Ervin T. Rouse would be pleased). Don't expect to be able to sit still after viewing this one !
